Package: tennispreds
Title: ATP Men's Tennis Match-Outcome Predictor
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Mona", "Ascha", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Internal project (not a distributed package): the
    Tennis_Data_Prep pipeline carved into R/ pure functions plus a
    Plumber prediction API. This DESCRIPTION declares the lean runtime
    dependency contract -- only what R/ and api.R actually use -- and
    is the basis for the explicit renv lockfile. The legacy markdowns/
    notebooks pull in a much larger ML stack (keras, tidymodels,
    caret, ...); those are intentionally NOT locked here because they
    are being retired/migrated in refactor step 5.
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    naniar,
    stringr,
    lubridate,
    runner,
    fastDummies,
    here,
    plumber,
    xgboost
